\id TDX - Gela Translation Project
\h Lei Tete te hangagho
\toc1 Na lei Tete ilokana na Rongorongo Uto Vaolu Kara Hangagho ge Ko Bosa Tughua nimua na Huahuati
\toc2 Lei Tete te hangagho
\toc3 Lei Tete te hangagho
\mt2 Na lei Tete ilokana na
\mt1 Rongorongo Uto Vaolu
\mt2 Kara Hangagho ge Ko Bosa Tughua nimua na Huahuati
\is1 ?Ahei a God? ?Ivei te vagha God?
\ip Mark 10:27; 12:29–30; Luke 1:37; 6:35–36; John 4:23–24; Gehegehedira 14:14–17; 17:22–31; Rome 1:18–23; 11:33–36; 1 Corinth 8:4–6; 2 Corinth 1:3; 1 Timothy 1:17; 6:15–16; Rana Hebrew 4:13; 10:30–31; James 1:17; 1 Peter 1:14–17; 1 John 1:5; 4:7–12; 4:16; Jude1:24–25; Na Livu 4:8–11; 15:3–4.
\is1 ?Ahei te gonia na maramana mana lei totobo ilokana?
\ip Matthew 19:4; John 1:3; Gehegehedira 14:15; 17:24–26; 1 Corinth 8:6; Colosse 1:15–16; Rana Hebrew 1:2; 11:3; Na Livu 4:11.
\is1 ?Mana hava na maramana te ghaha so?
\ip Matthew 6:25–34; 10:29–31; Gehegehedira 14:15–17; Rome 8:28; 11:36; Colosse 1:17; Rana Hebrew 1:3; James 4:13–16.
\is1 ?Ahei a Jesus? ?Ivei te vagha Jesus?
\is2 A Jesus na Dalena God.
\ip Matthew 11:27–30; 16:13–17; Luke 1:35; John 1:1–18; 5:19–29; 6:35–40; 8:58; 11:25–27; 14:5–11; 17:1–5; 20:26–31; Gehegehedira 3:13–16; 4:10–12; Rome 1:3–4; 1 Corinth 3:11; 2 Corinth 4:4–6; 5:21; Galatia 4:4–5; Philippi 2:5–11; Colosse 1:15–20; 2:9–10; Rana Hebrew 1:1–14; 7:26–28; 1 John 2:1–2; 5:20; Na Livu 1:12–18; 19:11–16.
\is2 Gaia na tinoni tara vahua.
\ip Matthew 1:18–25; 2:1–23; Luke 1:26–38; 2:1–20; John 1:14; Galatia 4:4–5; Philippi 2:6–7; Rana Hebrew 2:14–18.
\is2 Gaia te taraira rana vure, me ke vavolara na lei vahaghi, me ke gonighi subo na butuli.
\ip Matthew 4:23–25; 7:28–29; 8:1–4; 8:5–13; 8:14–15; 8:23–27; 8:28–33; 9:1–7; 9:18–36; 11:1–6, 12:9–14; 12:22; 14:15–21; 14:22–32; 15:22–28; 15:32–38; 17:14–18; 20:29–34; 21:18–22; Mark 1:21–28; 7:32–37; 8:22–25; Luke 4:14–44, 5:4–8; 7:11–15; 13:10–13; 14:1–4; 17:12–14; 22:50–51; John 2:1–11; 4:46–54; 5:5–9; 9:1–7; 11:11–44; 20:30–31; 21:4–6; Gehegehedira 2:22, 10:36–38.
\is1 ?Ahei na Tarunga Tabu? ?Ivei te vagha na Tarunga Tabu?
\ip Matthew 28:19; Mark 1:9–11; 3:28–30; Luke 1:35; 3:16; 4:1; 11:13; 12:12 John 1:32–34; 3:5–8; 7:37–39; 14:15–17; 14:26; 15:26; 16:7–15; 20:19–23; Gehegehedira 1:4–5; 1:8; 2:1–18; 2:38–39; 4:31; 5:3–5; 8:14–17; 10:44–48; 13:2–4; 15:28; 16:7–10; 19:1–7; Rome 5:5; 7:6; 8:9–16; 8:26–27; 1 Corinth 2:4; 2:9–16; 3:16; 6:11; 6:19; 12:1–13; 2 Corinth 1:21–22; 5:5; 13:14; Galatia 3:2–5; 4:6; 5:16–18; 5:22–25; Ephesus 1:13–14; 1:17; 3:16; 4:3–4; 4:30.
\is1 ?Na hava te kalea Jesus?
\is2 Tara lotia mara detea ge ke mate.
\ip Matthew 26:47–68; 27:1–2; 27:11–31; Mark 14:43–65; 15:1–20; Luke 22:47–53; 22:63–71; 23:1–25; John 18:1–14; 18:19–24; 18:28–19:16.
\is2 Gaia tara patokia tana ghaivavala.
\ip Matthew 27:32–56; Mark 15:21–41; Luke 23:26–49; John 19:17–37.
\is2 Gaia tara tavughia tana vataluma ni beku.
\ip Matthew 27:57–66; Mark 15:42–47; Luke 23:50–56; John 19:38–42.
\is2 Gaia te tughuru olia tana mate, me subo na vure tara righia.
\ip Matthew 28:1–20; Mark 16:1–8; Luke 24:1–49; John 20:1–21:14; Gehegehedira 1:3–8; 2:24–32; 3:15; 4:10; 4:33; 10:39–43; 13:29–39; 17:2–3; 17:30–31; Rome 1:4; 4:24–25; 1 Corinth 15:3–8; 15:12–21; Na Livu 1:18.
\is2 Gaia te pulohi dato i kokou.
\ip Luke 24:50–51; Gehegehedira 1:9–11; 2:32–36; 5:30–31; Rome 8:34; Ephesus 1:20–23; Philippi 2:9–11; Rana Hebrew 1:3–11; 2:9; 4:14–16; 7:25–26; 10:12–14; 1 Peter 3:22.
\is1 ?Na hava na pukuna Jesus ge mate?
\ip Mark 10:45; John 3:16; Rome 4:25; 5:8; 1 Corinth 15:3–4; 2 Corinth 5:19–21; Galatia 3:13; 1 Timothy 2:5–6; Rana Hebrew 2:9; 9:28; 1 Peter 1:18–20; 2:24–25; 3:18; 1 John 2:2; Na Livu 5:8–10.
\is1 ?Na hava na ghanaghana ilokana God te vavolaghita?
\is2 Na mateana Jesus te talukehai na lei paluda.
\ip Matthew 26:26–29; Rome 3:25; 5:9–10; Ephesus 1:7; Rana Hebrew 9:11–14; 1 John 1:6–7; Na Livu 7:14–17.
\is2 God te talukehai na paluda.
\ip Gehegehedira 5:31; 10:43; 26:18; Ephesus 1:7; 4:32; Colosse 1:13–14; 2:13–14; Rana Hebrew 10:17–18; 1 John 1:8–10.
\is1 Ivei te ghaghua na tinoni te keha tana bona God te vavolaa?
\is2 Gaia te maemane tana matana God.
\ip Gehegehedira 13:38–39; Rome 1:16–17; 3:21–26; 5:1; 5:18–19; Galatia 2:16; 3:6–9; Titus 3:7.
\is2 Gaia te loghoa na vola vaolu.
\ip John 3:1–16; 5:19–29; 10:10; 11:25–26; 14:6; 17:2–3; 20:31; Rome 5:21; 6:5–14; 8:10–17; 2 Corinth 5:17; Galatia 2:20; Ephesus 2:1–6; Colosse 2:13; 3:1–4; 2 Timothy 1:10; Titus 3:4–7; 1 Peter 1:23; 1 John 5:11–13.
\is2 Gaia na Dalena God.
\ip John 1:12–13; Rome 8:14–17; Galatia 4:6–7; Rana Hebrew 12:5–11; 1 John 3:1–3.
\is1 Inau ke na tinoni uto tua. ?Me ghua God ge ke ghoi vavolau mughua?
\is2 Na lei tinoni udolu tara tangohahi.
\ip John 8:7–9; Rome 3:9–20; 3:23; 5:12; Galatia 3:22; 1 John 1:8–10.
\is2 Aeni na hava rana hahi te vaghara.
\ip Rome 1:18–32; 8:5–8; Galatia 5:19–21; Ephesus 2:1–3; 5:3–5; Colosse 3:5–10; James 4:17; 1 Peter 4:3; 1 John 3:4–5.
\is2 Rana vure tara loghoa mughua God te vavolara tana na totoro vania na paludira.
\ip Matthew 10:28; 13:41–42; John 3:18–20; 3:36; Gehegehedira 17:30–31; Rome 1:18–19; 6:23; Galatia 6:7–8; Colosse 3:5–6; 2 Thessalonica 1:7–9; Rana Hebrew 9:27; 10:26–31; 1 Peter 1:17; 4:3–5; Jude 7; Na Livu 20:11–15.
\is1 God te sule me loghoa na maana sule, mi nau te pile mu mua haba. ?Ivei tea ge ghanaghanau?
\ip John 3:16; Rome 5:8; 1 Timothy 2:3–6; 2 Peter 3:9; 1 John 4:9–10.
\is1 Inau na tinoni dika. ?Ivei tea God ke tangomana na talukehani na lei palugu soko?
\ip Gehegehedira 5:31; 10:43; 26:18; Ephesus 1:7; Colosse 1:13–14; 2:13–14; 1 Timothy 1:15–16; Rana Hebrew 10:17–18; 1 John 1:8–10.
\is1 ?Na hava tu gonia ge God ke vavolau mughua?
\is2 Inau tu tughulio mughua mu ku mua gonighi na lei nilabu dika.
\ip Matthew 4:17; Mark 6:12; Luke 13:1–5; 15:1–31; 24:45–47; Gehegehedira 2:37–40; 3:19–20; 17:29–31; 20:21; 26:19–20; 2 Corinth 7:8–11; 2 Peter 3:9; Na Livu 9:20–21.
\is2 Inau tu taluutunia mughua Jesus vamua ge ke vavolau.
\ip John 1:12; 3:15–18; 3:36; 6:47; 14:6; 20:31; Gehegehedira 4:12; 16:30–31; Rome 3:20–22; 10:9–10; Galatia 2:16; Ephesus 2:8–9.
\is1 ?Ivei te ghaghua inau tu puku ni ghilala God te vavolau?
\ip John 3:1–16; 5:19–29; 11:25–26; 14:6; 17:2–3; 20:31; Rome 8:10–17; 2 Corinth 5:17; Ephesus 2:1–6; Colosse 2:13; Titus 3:4–7; 1 John 5:11–13.
\is1 ?Na hava ku nia vuivuni ku gonia, itaeni nau na tinoni taluutuni tua?
\is2 Inau tu tughulio tana lei nilabu dika ge ku taonighi na lei nilabu maemane.
\ip Luke 13:3; Gehegehedira 26:20; Rome 12:1-2; Colosse 3:5-17, 1 Thessalonica 4:7; Ephesus 4:28; 2 Peter 3:9
\is2 Inau tara vulitabuu.
\ip Matthew 28:18–20; John 3:22; 4:1–2; Gehegehedira 2:37–42; 8:12; 8:36–38; 10:44–48; 16:14–15; 16:31–33; 19:1–7; 22:12–16; Rome 6:1–4; Galatia 3:26–27; Colosse 2:12; 1 Peter 3:20–22.
\is2 Inau tu idumia na Rongorongo Uto udolu ge ku ghilala utunia God mana hava gaia te liona inau ku gonighi.
\ip Matthew 4:1–4; 5:17–20; 22:29; John 8:31–32; 20:31; Gehegehedira 20:32; Rome 15:4; 16:26; Colosse 3:16; 1 Thessalonica 2:13; 1 Timothy 4:13; 2 Timothy 3:14–17; Rana Hebrew 4:12; 1 Peter 1:22–25; 2 Peter 1:19–21; 2 John 9–10; Na Livu 1:3.
\is2 Inau tu vaukolu kolura na lei tinoni taluutuni ge kai holohabaa God.
\ip Matthew 18:19–20; Gehegehedira 2:41–47; Rome 12:4–8; Ephesus 1:22–23; 4:11–16; Colosse 3:15–17; 1 Timothy 4:13; Rana Hebrew 10:24–25.
\is2 Inau tu vaukolu kolura na lei tinoni ge kai ghania na Vanga Tabu.
\ip Matthew 26:26–30; Mark 14:22–26; Luke 22:14–20; 1 Corinth 10:14–22; 11:17–34.
\is2 Inau tu kokoeliulivuti vania God mu ku bosa vania nia na volagu.
\ip Matthew 6:5–13; 7:7–11; 18:19–20; Mark 1:35; 11:24–25; Luke 5:16; 6:12; 11:1–13; 18:1–8; 21:36; John 14:13–14; 15:7; 16:23–26; Rome 8:26–27; 12:12; Ephesus 2:18; 6:18; Philippi 4:6–7; Colosse 4:2; 1 Thessalonica 5:17; 1 Timothy 2:1–4; 2:8; 4:4–5; Rana Hebrew 4:16; 10:19–22; James 1:5–8; 4:2–3; 5:13–18; 1 Peter 4:7; 1 John 3:21–22; 5:14–15.
\is1 ?Na hava na kokoeliulivuti? ?Ivei te ghaghua inau tu kokoeliulivuti?
\ip Matthew 6:5–13; 7:7–11; 14:23; 18:19–20; Mark 1:35; 11:24–25; Luke 5:16; 6:12; 11:1–13; 18:1–8; 21:36; 22:32–45; John 14:13–14; 15:7; 16:23–26; 17:1–26; Gehegehedira 4:24–31; 16:25; Rome 1:9–10; 8:26–27; 10:1–2,12:12; 15:30–33; 2 Corinth 12:7–10; Ephesus 1:15–20; 2:18; 3:14–21; 6:18-20; Philippi 1:3–11; 4:6–7; Colosse 1:9–12; 4:2-4; 1 Thessalonica 3:9–13, 5:17; 2 Thessalonica 1:11–12; 3:1–2; 1 Timothy 2:1–4; 2:8; 4:4–5; Rana Hebrew 4:16; 5:7; 7:25, 10:19–22; James 1:5–8; 4:2–3; 5:13–18; 1 Peter 4:7; 1 John 3:21–22; 5:14–15.
\is1 ?Na pukuna inau na tinoni taluutuni tua ke, ivei te ghaghua inau tu tughui na nilabugu mana ghanaghanagu?
\is2 Inau ku dolovia God.
\ip Matthew 5:43–48; 22:34–40; Mark 12:28–34; Luke 10:25–37; John 14:21; 1 John 5:1-3; 1 Corinth 16:14; 1 Peter 1:8; 1 John 4:20–21.
\is2 Inau ku taonia God ma Jesus na pukuna gaia nigua na Lord.
\ip John 14:15; 14:21; 14:23–24; 15:10–17; Rome 13:8–10; 1 Peter 1:14–16; 1 John 2:3–8; 3:22–24; 2 John 1:5–6.
\is2 Inau ku kabu te vagha Jesus.
\ip John 13:34–35; 14:27; Rome 12:9–13; Galatia 5:22–26; Colosse 3:12–17; 1 Thessalonica 5:16–18.
\is2 Inau ku holoutoa God haia na pukuna na hava te gonighi vaniu.
\ip Luke 17:11–19; John 6:11; Rome 1:21; Ephesus 5:20; Philippi 4:4–7; Colosse 2:7; 3:17; 4:2; 1 Thessalonica 5:18; 1 Timothy 2:1; 4:4–5
\is2 Inau ku dolovira rana vure keha.
\ip Matthew 5:43–48; 22:34–40; Mark 12:28–34; Luke 10:25–37; John 13:34–35; 15:12–17; Rome 12:9–10; 13:8–10; 1 Corinth 13:1–3; 16:14; Galatia 5:13–15; 1 Thessalonica 4:9–10; 1 Peter 2:17; 4:8; 1 John 2:9–11; 3:11–18; 4:7–21; 5:1-3.
\is2 Inau ku hangara rana keha.
\ip Matthew 5:43–48; 6:1–4; 7:12; 22:34–40; 25:31–46; Mark 12:28–34; Luke 3:10–11; 6:38; 10:25–37; John 13:34–35; 14:21, 15:12–17; Gehegehedira 11:27–30; Rome 12:9–10; 13:8–10; 1 Corinth 10:24; 13:1–3; 16:14; 2 Corinth 8:1–15; 9:1–15; Galatia 5:13–15; 6:9–10; 1 Thessalonica 4:9–10; Philippi 4:14–19; Rana Hebrew 10:24; 13:1–3; 13:16; James 1:27; 2:15–16; 1 Peter 1:8; 4:8; 1 John 2:9–11; 3:11–18; 4:7–21. 5:3;
\is2 Inau ku talumuri.
\ip Matthew 5:3–12; 18:1–5; Luke 14:7–11; 18:9–14; Rome 12:16; 1 Corinth 4:7; 2 Corinth 10:17–18; Ephesus 4:2; Philippi 2:3–11; Colosse 3:12–13; James 4:5–16; 1 Peter 5:5–7.
\is2 Inau ku talumava arahei tara vunaghi pungisiu.
\ip Matthew 22:15–22; Gehegehedira 5:27–29; Rome 13:1–7; 1 Timothy 2:1–4; Rana Hebrew13:17; Titus 3:1; 1 Peter 2:13–17.
\is1 ?Na hava na lei totobo ku bei gonighi?
\is2 Inau ku mua dolovighi na rongo mana lei lologho.
\ip Matthew 6:19–21; 6:24–34; Luke 12:13–21; 12:32–34; Gehegehedira 20:35; 1 Timothy 6:6–10; 6:17–19; Rana Hebrew 13:5–6, James 2:1–9; 5:1–6.
\is2 Inau ku mua holohaba na lei god keha pu ku ghanaghana mavara na lei keramo.
\ip Matthew 4:10; Gehegehedira 17:22–31; 1 Corinth 5:11; 6:9–11; 8:1–13; 10:1–22; 2 Corinth 6:14–18; Galatia 5:19–21; 1 Thessalonica 1:9–10; 1 John 5:21; Na Livu 21:8; 22:15.
\is2 Inua ku mua nongira na lei keramo ge kara hangau pa kara dikalara rana keha nia didira maana.
\ip Matthew 4:10; Gehegehedira 17:22–31;; 1 Corinth 5:11; 6:9–11; 8:1–13; 10:1–22; 2 Corinth 6:14–18; Galatia 5:19–21; 1 Thessalonica 1:9–10; 1 John 5:21; Na Livu 21:8; 22:15.
\is2 Inau ku mua vasukaghighi na lei maumanu vanira na lei keramo.
\ip Matthew 9:13; Mark 12:33; Rome 12:1; Rana Hebrew 9:6–10:18.
\is2 Inau ku bei inubulebule.
\ip Rome 13:13; 1 Corinth 5:9–11; 6:9–11; Galatia 5:19–21; Ephesus 5:18; 1 Timothy 3:1–3; Titus 1:7; 1 Peter 4:3–5.
\is2 Inau ku bei kabalaghi.
\ip Matthew 5:27–30 John 8:2–11; Rome 13:8–10; 1 Corinth 5:9–11; 6:9–20; Galatia 5:19; Ephesus 5:3; Colosse 3:5–6; 1 Thessalonica 4:1–8; Rana Hebrew 13:4; Jude 1:7.
\is2 Inau ku bei kiko.
\ip Ephesus 4:25; Colosse 3:9; 1 Peter 3:10; John 8:44; Na Livu 21:8; 22:15.
\is2 Inau ku bei gito.
\ip Matthew 15:19, 19:18; Luke 19:8; Rome 13:9; 1 Corinth 6:9-10; Ephesus 4:28; James 5:4; 1 Peter 4:15; Na Livu 9:21
\is2 Inau ku bei bosadika.
\ip Ephesus 4:29; 5:4; Philippi 4:8; Colosse 3:8; 1 Timothy 4:12; James 1:26; 3:9–10.
\is2 Inau ku bei lavitughu tana bona rana vure tara diki gonia vaniu na dika.
\ip Matthew 6:12–15; 18:21–35; Mark 11:25; Luke 17:3–4; Rome 12:17–21; Ephesus 4:31–32; Colosse 3:13.
\is2 Inau ku mua beto na doloviadira lei tinoni. Sakai vamua inau tu rutu vania na dika na tinoni te gonia ke, inau ku dolovia mughua na tinoni keri.
\ip Galatia 5:22–23; Ephesus 4:26; Colosse 3:8; 3:13; James 1:19–20.
\is1 ?Ivei tea ge ku ghilala na hava te uto pe dika?
\ip Rome 1:18–32; 1 Corinth 6:9–11; Galatia 5:19–21; Ephesus 5:3–5; Colosse 3:5–10; James 4:17; 1 Peter 4:3; 1 John 2:15–17; 3:4–5.
\is1 ?Na hava na holohoru?
\ip Matthew 16:13–20; Gehegehedira 2:41–42; Rome 12:4–8; 1 Corinth 12:12–30; Ephesus 1:22–23; 2:19–22; 4:1–16; Colosse 1:18; Rana Hebrew 10:24–25; 1 Peter 2:4–10; Na Livu 19:5–10.
\is2 ?Ivei te vaghara na lei taluutuni uto tana holohoru?
\ip Matthew 16:13–20; Gehegehedira 2:41–42; Rome 12:4–8; 1 Corinth 12:12–30; Ephesus 1:22–23; 2:19–22; 4:1–16; Colosse 1:18; Rana Hebrew 10:24–25; 1 Peter 2:4–10; Na Livu 19:5–10.
\is2 ?Ivei te vaghara na lei huhuli uto tana holohoru?
\ip Matthew 28:18–20; Luke 22:24–27; Gehegehedira 6:1–6; 14:23; 20:17–35; 1 Thessalonica 2:1–12; 1 Timothy 3:1–13; 4:1–16, Titus 1:5–9, 1 Peter 5:1–4.
\is2 ?Ivei kara nea na lei tinoni tana holohoru kara nira kikinima rana tinoni huhuli?
\ip 1 Corinth 9:14; Galatia 6:6; 1 Thessalonica 5:12–13; 1 Timothy 5:17–22; Rana Hebrew 13:7; 13:17.
\is1 ?Ivei te vagha na binaboli tana taluutuni?
\is2 ?Ivei te ghaghua na manetaulaghi tana taluutuni?
\ip Matthew 19:4–6; 1 Corinth 7:1–16; Ephesus 5:21–33; Colosse 3:18–19; Titus 2:3–5; Rana Hebrew 13:4; 1 Peter 3:1–7.
\is2 ?Ivei te ghaghua na vaivine taulaghi tana taluutuni?
\ip Matthew 19:4–6; 1 Corinth 7:1–16; Ephesus 5:21–33; Colosse 3:18–19; Titus 2:3–5; Rana Hebrew 13:4; 1 Peter 3:1–7.
\is2 Na vinekamagu mi nau toro pepo talau. ?Ivei tea ge koro vilivoka na taugu mi nau?
\ip Matthew 5:31–32, 19:3–9; Luke 16:18; Rome 7:2–3; 1 Corinth 7:10–16.
\is2 Na vinekamagu te mua taluutuni. ?Ivei tea inau ku tuvavokaa keri ge ku tauna siki sakai te taluutuni?
\ip 1 Corinthians 7:12-16
\is2 Inau tu liona ge ku tauna na vaivine, hauva na vaivine eni te mua taluutunia Jesus. ?Ivei tea te uto so ge ku tauna?
\ip 2 Corinthians 6:14-15
\is2 ?Ivei te ghaghua na lei gari tana taluutuni?
\ip Matthew 15:3–6; Luke 2:51; Ephesus 6:1–3; Colosse 3:20; 1 Timothy 5:4; 5:8; Rana Hebrew 12:7–11.
\is2 ?Ivei te ghaghua ge ku righitaonia na dalegu?
\ip Ephesus 6:1–4; Colosse 3:20–21; 1 Timothy 3:4–5.
\is2 ?Ivei te ghaghua ge ku holopangotira na tinagu mana tamagu?
\ip Matthew 15:3–6; Ephesus 6:1–3; Colosse 3:20; 1 Timothy 5:4–8.
\is2 ?Ivei te ghaghua na lei tinoni tara mua loghoa na binaboli, te vaghara na lei matesasani mana daleisamu?
\ip Gehegehedira 6:1; Rome 7:2–3; 1 Corinth 7:39–40; 1 Timothy 5:3–16; James 1:27.
\is1 ?Ivei tea God te righitaonira rana taluutuni ge kara mua loghoa siki vahola haia?
\ip Rome 8:18–25; 8:28; 2 Corinth 1:4; 4:16–18; James 1:2–4; 1 Peter 1:6–9; 2:19–21; 5:8–10.
\is1 ?Na hava ku gonia tana bona inau tu tabotabo ge ku gonia siki totobo dika?
\ip Matthew 4:1–11; 6:13; 26:41; Luke 22:31–32; John 17:14–19; Rome 8:31–39; 12:12; 16:19–20; 1 Corinth 10:12–13; 16:13; 2 Corinth 12:7–10; Ephesus 3:20–21; 6:10–18; Philippi 4:13; 1 Thessalonica 3:5–8; 2 Thessalonica 3:3; 2 Timothy 1:7–8; Rana Hebrew 2:18; 4:14–16; 12:1–2; James 1:12–15, 4:7; 1 Peter 1:5; 5:8–11; 1 John 4:4; 5:3–5; Na Livu 12:7–12.
\is2 ?Na hava ku gonia tana bona Satan te tabotabo ge ke dikalau?
\ip Matthew 4:1–11; 6:13; 13:19; Luke 4:1–13; 22:3–4, 22:31–32; John 8:42–44; 17:14–19; Rome 16:19–20; 1 Corinth 16:13; 2 Corinth 2:10–11; 4:4; 11:13–15; 12:7–10; Ephesus 2:2; 3:20–21; 6:10–18; 1 Thessalonica 3:5–8; 2 Thessalonica 3:3; James 4:7–8; 1 Peter 5:8–11; 1 John 4:4; Na Livu 12:7–12, 20:1–3; 20:10.
\is2 ?Na hava ku gonia ke vagha inau tu vuivuni ge ku tangohahi?
\ip Luke 15:11–24; Rome 6:1–23; 1 John 1:9–2:2; James 4:7–10; Rana Hebrew 12:1–2; Na Livu 3:19–20.
\is2 Inau tu tabotabo ge ku kabu maemane, hauva tu tumuhoru talau. ?Ivei tea God ke hangau?
\ip Matthew 18:19–20; 28:19–20; John 14:16–23; Rome 8:35–39; 2 Corinth 6:16–18; Ephesus 3:17–19; Philippi 4:13; Colosse 2:6–7; 2 Thessalonica 3:16; Rana Hebrew 13:5–6.
\is1 ?Na hava ku gonia tana bona nigua na binaboli mi nau tai vahaghi?
\ip Matthew 4:23–25; 9:35; 11:2–5; Gehegehedira 3:1–6; 8:4–8; 19:11–16; 28:8–9; 1 Corinth 12:9; 12:29–30; 2 Corinth 12:7–10; 1 Timothy 5:23; 2 Timothy 4:20; James 5:14–15.
\is1 ?Na hava ku gonia tana bona na lei vahola kara kaleu?
\ip Rome 8:18–25; 8:28; 8:35–37; 12:12; 2 Corinth 1:3–5; 4:16–18; James 1:2–4; 1 Peter 1:3–9; 2:19–23; 5:8–10.
\is1 ?Na hava ku gonia tana bona kara gunaliu rana keha ma kara batobatou na pukuna tu taonia Jesus?
\ip Matthew 5:10–12; Mark 13:9–13; Luke 12:4–9; John 15:18–21; 16:1–4; Gehegehedira 5:41; Rome 8:35–37; 12:12–14; 12:17–21; 1 Corinth 4:11–13; 2 Corinth 4:8–11; 12:10; Philippi 1:28–29; 2 Thessalonica 1:4–8; 3:2–4; 2 Timothy 3:10–13; Rana Hebrew 10:32–39; 12:3–4; 1 Peter 3:13–17; 4:12–19; Na Livu 2:10.
\is1 Ivei tea rahei tara taluutunia Jesus, kara mataghunia na mate?
\ip John 6:39‑40, 11:17‑27, 14:1‑4; Rome 8:10‑11; 8:38‑39; 14:7‑9; 1 Corinth 15:12‑58; 2 Corinth 5:1‑10; Philippi 1:20‑24; 1 Thessalonica 4:13‑18; Rana Hebrew 2:14‑15; Na Livu 14:13; 21:1‑4, 22:1‑5.
\is1 ?Na hava ke kale tana ngiha?
\is2 Jesus ke oli mai tana maramana.
\ip Matthew 24:29–44; John 14:1–3; Gehegehedira 1:10–11; 3:19–21; Philippi 3:20–21; Colosse 3:4; 1 Thessalonica 1:9–10; 3:13; 4:13–5:11; 2 Thessalonica 1:6–10; 2:1–4; 1 Timothy 6:13–15; 2 Timothy 4:8; Rana Hebrew 9:28; 2 Peter 3:1–18; 1 John 3:1–3; Na Livu 1:7; 22:12–13.
\is2 Jesus Christ ke detera na lei tinoni soko na pukuna God te vahea na maana vania.
\ip Matthew 7:21–23; 16:24–27; 25:31–46; John 3:18–21; 5:24–29; Gehegehedira 17:30–31; Rome 2:1–11; 14:10–12; 1 Corinth 3:10–15; 4:5; 2 Corinth 5:9–10; 2 Thessalonica 1:5–10; Rana Hebrew 9:27–28; 10:26–31; 1 Peter 1:17; 4:3–5; Na Livu 20:11–15.
\is2 Arahei God te vavolara tua kara kabu kolua i kokou.
\ip Luke 12:32–34; John 14:1–3; 2 Corinth 5:1–8; Philippi 1:23; 1 Peter 1:4–5; Na Livu 4:1–11; 21:1–4; 21:22–22:5; 22:14–15.
\is2 Arahei God ke mua vavolara ke torora haia tana lake kasila.
\ip Matthew 10:28; 13:41–42; 47–50; 25:41; Luke 16:23–26; 2 Thessalonica 1:9; Na Livu 20:10–15; 21:8. 
